claim.claim-text:
14. A turbine nozzle 22 comprising: 
ceramic outer and inner bands; 
a pair of ceramic outer sections integrally joined to said outer band; 
a pair of ceramic inner sections integrally joined to said inner band in alignment with said outer sections to define a pair of vane aft segments bifurcated at an axial splitline; and 
a pair of metal vane forward segments adjoining respective ones of said vane aft segments along a radial splitline.
